# SDD (Iconify)

- Before implementing features, read [`SPEC.md`](../../SPEC.md) and [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md).
- Change requirements in `SPEC.md` first; update `TASKS.md` only for work-breakdown / checkboxes; then code.
- Do not invent API fields, asset filenames, sizes, or status codes.
- Prefer matching SPEC §2 matrix and §3 OpenAPI exactly.
- After finishing a slice, update checkboxes in `TASKS.md`.
- Keep diffs scoped to the active milestone; no unrelated refactors.
